cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CYBER, cs.SI, cs.SY. 

The paper focuses on developing intelligent systems using AI and machine learning to influence individual behavior and reduce transportation-related energy expenditure of a city. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories as they deal with AI and machine learning. The paper also incorporates ideas from economics, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CYBER, which deals with economic and game-theoretic aspects of cybersecurity. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel empirical evaluation framework, which could place it in cs.SI (social and information networks) or cs.SY (systems and control).
